    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰国内经济将增长，但央行警告称美国政策变化存在风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/ireland-s-economy-to-grow-but-us-policy-changes-a-risk-central-bank-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰央行周二上调了经济增长预期，但警告称，美国潜在的经济政策变化将给公共财政和经济带来重大的下行风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/ireland-s-economy-to-grow-but-us-policy-changes-a-risk-central-bank-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 07:05:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯高级将领在莫斯科爆炸中丧生</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/high-ranking-russian-general-killed-in-explosion-in-moscow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二凌晨，俄罗斯放射、化学和生物防御部队负责人在莫斯科的一次炸弹爆炸中丧生，这似乎是该国高级军事官员遭暗杀的罕见事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/high-ranking-russian-general-killed-in-explosion-in-moscow</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 06:28:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国执政党在尹永哲裁决前暂停任命法官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/yoon-s-party-tries-to-block-more-judges-ruling-on-his-ouster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国执政党正试图推迟任命宪法法院法官，此举可能是为了阻止反对派增加罢免被弹劾总统尹锡烈的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/yoon-s-party-tries-to-block-more-judges-ruling-on-his-ouster</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 06:04:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国和印度官员将在北京举行边界会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/top-china-india-officials-to-meet-in-beijing-for-border-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度和中国高级官员将在北京会晤，讨论两国边界争端，重启自 2020 年以来陷入停滞的有关该问题的正式谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/top-china-india-officials-to-meet-in-beijing-for-border-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 05:36:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本计划在福岛时代结束之际增加核电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/japan-aims-to-expand-nuclear-power-in-break-from-fukushima-era</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本政府将致力于增加核能的使用，放弃十年来减少对能源依赖的政策，并扭转2011年福岛核事故后实施的限制措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/japan-aims-to-expand-nuclear-power-in-break-from-fukushima-era</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 04:02:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>副总理辞职后特鲁多在加拿大摇摇欲坠</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/trudeau-government-teeters-in-canada-after-freeland-pens-scathing-resignation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的政府陷入危机，因为他最信任的副手、财政部长克里斯蒂亚·弗里兰于周一公布了一份措辞严厉的辞职信，这在最糟糕的时候让他的政府陷入了困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/trudeau-government-teeters-in-canada-after-freeland-pens-scathing-resignation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 03:01:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥在打击贩毒行动中逮捕两名毒枭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/mexico-arrests-two-drug-lords-in-operation-against-trafficking</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥当局在加强锡那罗亚州安全行动中逮捕了两名毒枭，该州深陷贩毒集团各派系之间暴力冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/mexico-arrests-two-drug-lords-in-operation-against-trafficking</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 02:21:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>玻利维亚检察官对埃沃·莫拉莱斯发出逮捕令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/bolivia-prosecutors-issue-arrest-warrant-for-evo-morales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玻利维亚检察官周一表示，因涉及一名 15 岁未成年人性虐待指控的调查，已对前总统埃沃莫拉莱斯发出了逮捕令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/bolivia-prosecutors-issue-arrest-warrant-for-evo-morales</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 00:55:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的豁免权主张未能结束纽约封口费案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-loses-bid-to-have-hush-money-case-tossed-over-immunity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普未能说服法官以总统豁免权为由撤销对其在纽约封口费案中的定罪，但由于这位当选总统继续对判决提出质疑，目前尚不清楚该案是否仍将进入宣判阶段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-loses-bid-to-have-hush-money-case-tossed-over-immunity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 23:44:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政治不确定性拖累法国经济增长前景放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/france-s-growth-prospects-weaken-as-political-uncertainty-weighs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙任命法国一年内第四位总理几天后，法国央行下调了国内增长预期，央行称政治动荡拖累了家庭和企业信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/france-s-growth-prospects-weaken-as-political-uncertainty-weighs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
